    <p><b>From the North:</b></p>
    <p>From Junction 6 of the M20 take the A229 Maidstone to Hastings road via Loose and Linton.  2 miles out of Linton village with the Stile Bridge Inn on your right, take the B2079 towards Marden.  Take the 1st turning on the left, Battle Lane, for 500 yards until the road meets St Ann’s Green Lane.  Opposite you is Summerhill Farmhouse and the parking for Orchard Retreat is via the tarmac drive to the left of the house.</p>
    <p><b>From a southerly direction</b></p>
    <p>Take the A229 to Staplehurst.  At the traffic lights/cross roads take the Marden Road to the T-junction of Park Road and Battle Lane.  Turn right and over the railway bridge.  We are 1 mile from the railway bridge on the left and next door to a two kiln Oast house.  Turn left into the tarmac drive of Summerhill Farmhouse to parking for Orchard Retreat.</p>

